{
  "text": "Although the expression of the AUTS2 gene might not be equal between brain tissue and LCL, the cause of this inconsistency is needed for further research. [CITATION_1] However, in any event, these studies suggest that the rs6943555 variants may influence transcriptional activity and expression of the AUTS2 gene.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "207158257"
